---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Social Proof for Doulas — Collect & Display Client Testimonials | SocialProof.dev">
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">For Doulas</div>
        <h1>The most meaningful testimonials in any industry — make sure they're visible</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">When families hire a birth or postpartum doula, the stakes couldn't be higher. They need to trust you completely. Authentic client testimonials are the most powerful thing on your website.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="problem">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>New parents will choose their doula based on what other parents say</h2>
        <p>Families searching for a birth doula don't make this decision lightly. They look at your website, they read every word, and then they look for proof — stories from real families you've supported through one of the most vulnerable moments of their lives.</p>
        <p>The reviews exist in their heads. They just need a gentle, easy way to share them.</p>
        <p>SocialProof gives you a simple link to send in your postpartum follow-up — when gratitude is fresh and real. No login, no friction, just an honest 60-second review that could be the thing that convinces the next anxious parent to choose you.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="benefits">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for trust-based practices like doula work</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>💌 Gentle to request, easy to give</h3>
            <p>Include your link in your postpartum check-in email. No login, no account — just a simple form that takes a minute to complete, even for a sleep-deprived new parent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🔒 You control what's published</h3>
            <p>Every testimonial is reviewed by you before it appears on your site. You protect privacy — only publish what the client is comfortable sharing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📸 Faces make trust real</h3>
            <p>Optional photo uploads let clients attach a photo, making their testimonial feel personal and authentic — not anonymous text.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🌐 Works on any website platform</h3>
            <p>Whether you're on Squarespace, WordPress, or a custom site — add one script tag and your widget is live.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🎯 Collect for both birth and postpartum work</h3>
            <p>Create separate collection links for birth doula and postpartum doula services. Organize testimonials by service type in your dashboard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>⭐ Optional star ratings</h3>
            <p>Give families the option to leave a 5-star rating — builds visual trust and SEO-indexed review signals on your own domain.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sample-widget">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What it looks like on your site</h2>
        <div class="widget-preview">
          <blockquote>
            <p>"Having Sofia at our birth changed everything. She was calm when I wasn't, she advocated when I couldn't speak, and she helped my partner know exactly how to support me. I would hire her a thousand times over and recommend her to every family I know."</p>
            <footer>— Emma R., Portland OR · ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <p>This is the kind of testimonial that books your next client — and it's already sitting in your past clients' hearts.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready in minutes, pays off for years</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li><strong>Create a free account</strong> at app.socialproof.dev</li>
          <li><strong>Copy your collection link</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Add it to your postpartum check-in email</strong> — send it once to all past clients</li>
          <li><strong>Approve testimonials</strong> through your dashboard</li>
          <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your website — one line of code</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Doula-specific questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What if a client wants to stay anonymous?</h3>
            <p>The form has a name field, but you can display just a first name, initials, or any version of the credit the client is comfortable with. You control what appears publicly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I collect testimonials from clients years ago?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. Send your link to former clients anytime. Many will be happy to share something they've been meaning to say.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is the link reusable for all clients?</h3>
            <p>Yes — one link works for everyone. You don't create a new link per client. Just share it in every follow-up.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>My website is on Squarespace — does this work?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Add a Code Block to any Squarespace page and paste your widget script tag. The widget renders beautifully within your site design.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The families you've supported want to help other families find you</h2>
        <p>Give them an easy way. Start collecting testimonials today — free, no credit card.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free today</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget · No credit card required</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
